item.title: Few questions [PI]
item.dc:creator: @C_Imbued C++ Imbued
item.description:
@C_Imbued wrote:

[quote=“gangstaboy:D, post:1, topic:413209”]1. how do i change the welcome message … i have changed the one in server.java but that hasn’t seemed to work (client sided maybe?)
2. how do i change the name of the teleports
3. where do i edit my quest list from?
4. how do i find out which case something is?[/quote]

Answer 1: Serverside src/server/model/players/client.java Search: Welcome
Answer 2: Serverside src/server/model/players/playerAssistant.java Search: handleLoginText
Answer 3: Quest tab can be either serversided or clientsided If clientsided then rsinterface.java serverside client.java under public void process()
